text: Lapua is a city in Southern Ostrobothnia, Finland. It had almost 14,700 people living there in January 2014. The municipalities next to it are Alajärvi, Kauhava, Kuortane, Lappajärvi and Seinäjoki. == Other websites == * Perhekoon kaypunki Category:Cities in Finland Category:Municipalities of South Ostrobothnia
